snippet.title: AQUAMAN STAR AMBER HEARD ROLE REDUCED???
snippet.description:
It's being told that Amber's role in the upcoming sequel of Aquaman to be reduced as they bring in a new character to take her place to be a new plan for in case Amber Heard's accusations fall to the ground. I'm sort of surprised Warner bros. finally pulled their head out of their ass to finally get an understanding that more than 1 million consumers don't want Heard involved in future DCEU projects.
